{"tid":1628423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"以前不嬲都係罷食，搞元氣飲下綠茶。而家變左裝修。","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:10:11.000Z","uid":34174,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0fad77430a33d97520121459edced06991daf1dd","tid":1628423,"uid":34174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"裝唔裝修，唔係為左手足，唔係為左好唔好睇<br />\n係要諗下自己 做咁多野既價值係咩<br />\n<br />\n如果裝修係岩既路，咁一開始就裝修就得啦？<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日好明顯係有人帶風向，甚至係有狗混左入黎破壞，政府呢三日既劇本就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n最後，不過其實我都係核彈都唔割，你覺得自己做緊既野係岩就得，只係想每個人行動前諗清楚，呢幾日好易俾人帶到風向。"},{"pid":"981d3278299c88defbf72a54d394037ffb6cbcf5","tid":1628423,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"講撚左兩日仲講哩個topic"},{"pid":"b4fd389da44de837689234557459876b9b514f62","tid":1628423,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"超國泰俾共產黨迫害又唔見藍絲屌共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5961b2123eb3a2211402998fe7663420d1911df6","tid":1628423,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"過左兩日，成績表都出埋，重講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241da86770a6ce07a982bdd4f3d40c5a1ec4abfa","tid":1628423,"uid":292131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5961b2123eb3a2211402998fe7663420d1911df6","tid":1628423,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"過左兩日，成績表都出埋，重講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:07:06.000Z","msg":"屎忽痕拎黎講嘛<br />\n又要質疑又帶頭盔唔割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/do